http://www.recoverlostpassword.com/products/asteriskpasswordrecovery.html
Asterisk Password Recovery is a universal password recovery tool that allows you to shows passwords hidden under asterisks in password fields! It uncovers hidden passwords from password dialog boxes, Internet Explorer web pages and ActiveX controls.
